Whoa. Viral edit: the world is a crazy place right now. Most of it is beyond our control. Here are two cheap and simple things that can get us on the right track:
- Be kind to people. We’re all fighting some kind of fight.
- Wash your hands and cover your mouth when you cough. Wear a mask if you have any symptoms. We’re not out of the woods yet. A new strain could be right around the corner.
- Enjoy every day. Treat yourself to nice things and let your loved ones know they’re loved. 
- If you have a pet, give ‘em some love. You’re aware of the whole world. To them, you’re their world.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/0XXXqhO</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CloakedFigure25]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Feeding apparatus for little dragons....a never ending supply</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NJCxEYU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KgD6Yd7.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NJCxEYU</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[iwasdoingfinelurking]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>new zealand from the iss</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/YH33Z6A</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SqhdwDU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/YH33Z6A</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheRainbowegoSweet007]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Troll people</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/tf4LvHS</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wPFyPXh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/tf4LvHS</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[JoshMeme]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>It's the single most important issue</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/2xDy0AF</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ylYcsTA.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/2xDy0AF</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[JayAdan]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Origin story</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Mf7mtkl</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KNQ3VYQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Mf7mtkl</guid><dc:creator><![CDA